# ----------------------------------------
# Together AI: https://api.together.xyz/v1
#   - Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct
#   - meta-llama/Llama-3.3-70B-Instruct
#
# OpenRouter: https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
#   - qwen/qwen-2.5-coder-32b-instruct
#   - anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet
#
# LOCAL (vLLM via start_vllm.sh — set SCAGENT_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8000/v1):
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Downloaded and ready to serve:
#   Qwen3-32B                 - Best overall: 40K ctx, strong reasoning + thinking mode
#   Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct - Coding-focused, 128K ctx
#   Qwen2.5-72B-Instruct      - Largest, but only 32K ctx (not recommended for scagent)
#   gemma-4-31b-it            - Google multimodal, 256K native ctx (needs 2+ GPUs)
#
# Examples:
#   bash start_vllm.sh Qwen/Qwen3-32B 8000 2
#   bash start_vllm.sh Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-32B-Instruct 8000 1
